==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Filtrate
<hw>Fil"trate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>That which has been
filtered; the liquid which has passed through the filter in the process
of filtration. Contrasted with <contr>retentate</contr>, the material
remaining on the filter.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Filtration</ent>⟦br⟧
